title: Little School of the Redwoods is looking for a qualified (pic)
text:
ad date: 10/13/2015 
Little School of the Redwoods is looking for a qualified preschool teacher/center substitutes. Minimum required 12 core ECE units as described in Title 22 as well as documented experience under a qualified teacher. Must be able to present a TB test, health screen and have background clearance. Applications are available at Del Norte Child Care Council, 212 K. Street. Please bring a copy of your transcripts. For further information, please call (707) 464-4174.
